SVN2FTP
=======

-------------
Configuration
-------------
Create a new .INI file like "projects/sample.ini".

-------------
Usage Windows
-------------
cd C:\Your\Path\to\svn2ftp\bin
svn2ftp -c ../projects/project.ini -r 175:HEAD
svn2ftp -c ../projects/project.ini -r 163

If you did not add the PHP directory to you PATH
environment variable, you've to use "php svn2ftp.php"
instead of "svn2ftp".

-----------
Usage Linux
-----------
cd /your/path/to/svn2ftp/bin
php svn2ftp.php -c ../projects/project.ini -r 175:HEAD
php svn2ftp.php -c ../projects/project.ini -r 163

----
Hint
----
Add the "bin" directory to your PATH environment variable.